                    <span class="breadcrumb-trail"><a href="/us/conditions#attention-deficithyperactivity">Attention Deficit/Hyperactivity</a></span>
                    &nbsp;>&nbsp;
                    <span class="breadcrumb-trail">Attention-Deficit/Hyperactivity Disorder, Teen</span>
            </div>

